The government does NOT give away free money with no catch, or way to get reimbursed in the future. That said, how long do you think 1,200 will actually last, even if you are a single parent with one child?
Yes, it is a help, but a very small bandage on an enormous wound.
The citizens also need free health services, and testing!
The only way to combat this illness, and the economy is to afford people the testing, and health care, it's as simple as that, though this is not a simple illness...
If your health care systems do not provide for the well being of your Medical personal, lack provisions, affordable insurance, we can expect economic disasters, as well as millions of unnecessary deaths in the future.
Remember what grandma used to say, When you have your health, you have everything!
